<p><img title=\"Prophet Daniiel’s Mausoleum in Samarkand\" src=\"images/sights/prophet-daniiels-mausoleum.jpg\" alt=\"Prophet Daniiel’s Mausoleum in Samarkand\" width=\"550\" height=\"446\" /></p>
